e magic. Even better, it&#x2019;s the best place to visit in Portugal for wine; there are lots of beautiful wine estates with traditional farmhouses where you can stay for the night.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read more:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/portugal\/douro-valley-portugal\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">The complete Douro region travel guide<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12130434\/douro-valley2.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-58883 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12130434\/douro-valley2.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12130434\/douro-valley2-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12130434\/douro-valley2-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12130434\/douro-valley2-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12130434\/douro-valley2-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12130434\/douro-valley2-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12130434\/douro-valley2-144x180.jpg 144w, https: