e3-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12130746\/porto-bridge3-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12130746\/porto-bridge3-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12130746\/porto-bridge3-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12130746\/porto-bridge3-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12130746\/porto-bridge3-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12130746\/porto-bridge3-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12130746\/porto-bridge3-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12130746\/porto-bridge3-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12130746\/porto-bridge3-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12130746\/porto-bridge3-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12130746\/porto-bridge3.jpg 1281w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12130746\/porto-bridge3-20x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12130746\/porto-bridge3-540x810.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-9-bookstore-of-porto\">9. Bookstore of Porto<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/portugal\/porto-things-to-do\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">city trip to Porto<\/a> wouldn&#x2019;t be complete without visiting <a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/portugal\/livraria-lello-porto\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Livraria Lello: the famous bookstore of Porto<\/a>! The story goes that when JK Rowling lived in Porto, she came here often and used the book store as inspiration for the Harry Potter novels. You&#x2019;ll definitely feel those vibes when you enter the store, with its curved staircases, ruby red carpets, and endless bookshelves. <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>More about: <a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/portugal\/livraria-lello-porto\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Livraria Lello, Porto Bookstore<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12103516\/Livraria-Lello-porto2.jpg\" alt=\"Livraria Lello porto\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Livraria Lello porto\" class=\"wp-image-58850 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12103516\/Livraria-Lello-porto2.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12103516\/Livraria-Lello-porto2-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-