\">Visiting Porto<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>This is the perfect place to come and cozy up on a windy day in Porto and take some amazing photos. The atmosphere and the stories of this beautiful place make it one of the best places to visit in Portugal.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/portugal\/porto-city-trip\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Top things to do in Porto!<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<p><strong>Note:<\/strong> The bookstore is incredibly popular, and there is always a queue to get in. Because of this, it&#x2019;s a good idea to book your tickets in advance or book an organized tour that allows you to skip the queue completely.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12103505\/Livraria-Lello-porto1-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"Livraria Lello porto\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Livraria Lello porto\" class=\"wp-image-58848 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12103505\/Livraria-Lello-porto1-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12103505\/Livraria-Lello-porto1-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/12103505\/Livraria-